ques.p: To ask the Secretary of State for Justice what the reasons were for the dismissals of each of the (a) prison officers, (b) senior officers and (c) principal officers from each of the Welsh prisons in (i) 2005, (ii) 2006 and (iii) 2007. [Official Report, 7 January 2008, Vol. 470, c. 1MC.]
Question number missing in Hansard, possibly truncated question.

reply.p: Information on the reasons for dismissal of each of the officers dismissed from Welsh Prisons in 2005, 2006 and 2007 is shown in the list. Due to the different grading structure in public sector and contracted prisons it is not possible to break down the information by grade.
Failure to comply with operational procedures
Failure to notify company of arrest and subsequent charges
Failure to carry out roll count
Making untrue statements with intent on deceiving or defrauding the company
Failure to comply with operational procedures (x3)
Inappropriate and unprofessional behaviour towards a prisoner
